  "title": "Xtra Light Croatian Vegetable Stir fry",
  "description": "A light and healthy Croatian dish featuring stir-fry vegetables, cooked to perfection in a hot-pot vessel, perfect for a solo dinner. This flexitarian-friendly recipe uses sous-vide cooking for tender vegetables.",
