  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the hot-pot vessel to 180 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a bowl, toss the broccoli, carrots, bell peppers, onions, and mushrooms with olive oil, garlic, and paprika.",
    "Place the vegetable mixture in a sous-vide bag and seal.",
    "Cook the vegetables in the hot-pot vessel for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the vegetables from the bag and stir-fry in the hot-pot vessel for 5 minutes.",
    "Char the vegetables by increasing the heat to 200 degrees Fahrenheit for 2 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
